sequenceDiagram
    actor Responder
    actor Requester
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Email as Resend Email

    Responder->>Browser: Click "Cancel My Response"
    Browser->>API: DELETE /api/requests/{id}/respond/{responseId}
    API->>DB: Validate: responder owns this response
    API->>DB: Response.delete(responseId)
    DB-->>API: Deleted
    API->>Email: sendRequestClosedToResponderEmail(requester)
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
